Package: dailymet
Type: Package
Title: Utility Functions to Model Daily Meteorological Variables
Version: 0.1.5 
Author: Yves Deville  
Maintainer: Yves Deville <deville.yves@alpestat.com>
Description: Provide utility functions to model meteorological variables
    on a daily basis with emphasis on the extremes and Peaks Over Threshold
    (POT) models.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0), extRemes, quantreg, NHPoisson, ggplot2, scales
Imports: methods, nieve, utils, data.table
Suggests: NSGEV, leaflet, knitr, rmarkdown
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
